description: Quattro Exploration and Production Ltd. engages in the exploration and development of oil and natural gas reserves primarily in south central Saskatchewan and central Alberta, Western Canada. It holds interests in two active production operations in NE British Columbia and East Central Alberta; and one developing operation in SW Saskatchewan. The company was formerly known as Life Sciences Institute Inc. and changed its name to Quattro Exploration and Production Ltd. in October 2011. Quattro Exploration and Production Ltd. was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Leonard B. Van Betuw B.Sc.
